    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi regis aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> gratis Dei <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Convenit regali magnificentiae in
                        necessitatibus subvenire alterius, et racionabilibus peticionibus nostrorum
                        fidelium assensum prebere, quatinus id agendo premium aeternae
                        remunerationis mereatur accipere. Ideoque noverit omnium fidelium sanctae
                        Dei Aecclesiae nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum universitas,
                        domnum <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Consiliarius_regis #Archbishops #fidelisOf"><name
                                ref="Ildoinus">Hildoinum</name></persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/221">sancte <placeName ref="#places/147"
                                >Mediolanensis</placeName> aecclesiae</orgName> venerabilem <rs
                            key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopum</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Consiliarius_regis #Bishops #fidelisOf"
                            ref="#people/403">Vuidonem</persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/223">sanctae <placeName ref="#places/43"
                                >Placentine</placeName> aecclesiae</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs> excellentissimos <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fideles</rs> atque <rs key="#Consiliarius_regis">consiliarios</rs>
                        nostros nostram humiliter <rs key="#Intercessory">exorasse</rs>
                        celsitudinem, quatinus <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/1528"
                            >Anne</persName> quondam <rs key="#Queen">imperatrici</rs> relictae dive
                        memoriae <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> nostrae confirmationis preceptum
                        fieri iuberemus, per quod <rs key="#Curtes">duas cortes</rs> olym de <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property">iure regni nostri</rs> pertinentes, quas idem
                        imperator ei contulit, id sunt <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/2305">cortis in <placeName ref="#places/1313"
                                >Summolacu</placeName> que dicitur <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                >Ripa</placeName></geogName> et cortis altera que dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/2306"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                >Mauriatica</placeName></geogName>, confirmaremus et corroboraremus.
                        Quorum petitionibus annuentes, prout iuste et legaliter possumus,
                        confirmamus et corroboramus ei predictas duas cortes cum illarum
                        integritatibus, una cum <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, pascuis,
                            <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, salictis, sationibus, <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>,
                        vallibus, alpius, planitiaebus, cum <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et
                            ancillis utrisque sexus</rs>, cum <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldionibus et
                            aldianis</rs> et cum omnibus que dici vel nominari possunt ad ipsas duas
                        cortes iuste et legaliter respitientius in integrum, ut habeat, teneat
                        firmiterque possideat, habeatque potestatem tenendi, vendendi, donandi,
                        commutandi, alienandi, pro anima iudicandi, vel quicquid eius decreverit
                        animus faciendi, omnium hominum iniusta contradictione reota. Si qusi igitur
                        huius nostri precepti violator extiterit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras quinquaginta</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamere nostrae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem predictae Anne olym
                            imperatrici</rs> suisque heredibus. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligentiusque ab omnibus in perpetuum opservetur, manibus propriis
                        roborantes de anulo nostro subter anotari [i]ussimus. Signa serenissimorum
                        (MF) (MF) Hugonis et Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Abbots" ref="#people/1523">Gerlanni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi (SR) (SI D). data XVI
                        kal. iun., anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXXXVII, regni vero domni
                        Hugonis invictissimi regis X, et domni Lotharii item regis V, indic VIIII.
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/65">Papiae</placeName>. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
